692
00:42:19.066 --> 00:42:21.766
♪ Buck teeth
Bark in my claws

693
00:42:21.866 --> 00:42:24.067
♪ I'm a tree critter

694
00:42:26.367 --> 00:42:29.168
♪ Sticks and stones
are my bread and bones

695
00:42:29.168 --> 00:42:30.268
♪ I'm a tree critter

696
00:42:30.368 --> 00:42:33.569
- Triple G. what's up. baby?
